band- Releases: Dark Passion Play|accessdate=1 June 2010|publisher=Nightwish's Official Website|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601163448/http://www.nightwish.com/en/band/releases/details?id=27|archivedate=1 June 2010|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n{| width=\"100%\"\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| width=\"50%\" |\n\n===The band===\n*[[Anette Olzon]] \u2013 vocals (except Track 5)\n*[[Tuomas Holopainen]] \u2013 keyboards, backing vocals (on Track 5)\n*[[Marco Hietala]] \u2013 bass, acoustic guitar (on Track 10), vocals (on Tracks 1, 2, 4, 5, 10, and 12)\n*[[Emppu Vuorinen]] \u2013 electric and acoustic guitars\n*[[Jukka Nevalainen]] \u2013 drums, percussion\n\n===Main crew===\n* Tero Kinnunen- sound engineer\n* Mikko Karmila \u2013 mixing\n* Mika Jussila \u2013 mastering engineer\n* [[James Shearman]] \u2013 choir conducting\n* [[Pip Williams]] \u2013 orchestral arrangements\n|\n===Guest musicians===\n* [[London Philharmonic Orchestra]] \u2013 orchestral parts\n* [[Metro Voices]] \u2013 choir\n* [[Troy Donockley]] \u2013 [[bodhran]], [[uilleann pipes]], [[low whistle]] and [[tin whistle]] (on track 10, 11 and 13)\n* Guy Elliott \u2013 lead treble (on track 1)\n* Tom Williams \u2013 second treble (on track 1)\n* [[Nollaig Casey]] \u2013 violin (on track 11)\n* Zachary LaPorta \u2013 [[theremin]] (on tracks 1 and 11)\n* Senni Eskelinen \u2013 electric kantele (on track 11)\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of best-selling albums in Finland]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"FIN best dom\">{{Cite web<!--\n-->|url=http://www.ifpi.fi/tilastot/myydyimmat/kaikki/kotimaiset/albumit<!--\n-->|title=Kaikkien aikojen myydyimm\u00e4t kotimaiset albumit<!--\n-->|publisher=Musiikkituottajat \u2013 IFPI Finland<!--\n-->|language=Finnish<!--\n-->|accessdate=27 August 2013<!--\n-->}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FIN best for\">{{Cite web<!--\n-->|url=http://www.ifpi.fi/tilastot/myydyimmat/kaikki/ulkomaiset/albumit<!--\n-->|title=Kaikkien aikojen myydyimm\u00e4t ulkomais