n Institution}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1990}} |end_date={{End date|1991}} |event= [[Trudy Huskamp Peterson|Trudy H. Peterson]] |location= National Archives and Records Administration}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1991}} |end_date={{End date|1992}} |event= [[Frank G. Burke]] |location= University of Maryland}}\t\t\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1992}} |end_date={{End date|1993}} |event= [[Anne R. Kenney]] |location= Cornell University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1993}} |end_date={{End date|1994}} |event= [[Edie Hedlin]] |location= Consultant}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1994}} |end_date={{End date|1995}} |event= [[Maygene Daniels]] |location= National Gallery of Art}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1995}} |end_date={{End date|1996}} |event= [[Brenda Banks]] |location= Georgia Department of Archives and History}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1996}} |end_date={{End date|1997}} |event= Nicholas C. Burckel |location= Marquette University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1997}} |end_date={{End date|1998}} |event= William J. Maher |location= University of Illinois, Urbana-Champaign}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1998}} |end_date={{End date|1999}} |event= [[Luciana Duranti]] |location= University of British Columbia}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|1999}} |end_date={{End date|2000}} |event= H. Thomas Hickerson |location= Cornell University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2000}} |end_date={{End date|2001}} |event= Lee J. Stout |location= Pennsylvania State University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2001}} |end_date={{End date|2002}} |event= Steven L. Hensen |location= Duke University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2002}} |end_date={{End date|2003}} |event= Peter B. Hirtle |location= Cornell University Library}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2003}} |end_date={{End date|2004}} |event= Timothy L. Ericson |location= University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2004}} |end_date={{End date|2005}} |event= Randall C. Jimerson |location= Western Washington University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2005}} |end_date={{End date|2006}} |event= [[Richard Pearce-Moses]] |location= Arizona State Library Archives and Public Records}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2006}} |end_date={{End date|2007}} |event= [[Elizabeth W. Adkins]] |location= Ford Motor Company Archives}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2007}} |end_date={{End date|2008}} |event= [[Mark A. Greene]] |location= American Heritage Center, University of Wyoming}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2008}} |end_date={{End date|2009}} |event= Frank J. Boles |location= Clarke Historical Library}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2009}} |end_date={{End date|2010}} |event= Peter Gottlieb |location= Archives Division, Wisconsin Historical Society}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2010}} |end_date={{End date|2011}} |event= [[Helen Tibbo]] |location= School of Information and Library Science, University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2011}} |end_date={{End date|2012}} |event= [[Gregor Trinkaus-Randall]] |location= Massachusetts Board of Library Commissioners}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2012}} |end_date={{End date|2013}} |event= [[Jackie M. Dooley]] |location= OCLC Research}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2013}} |end_date={{End date|2014}} |event= [[Danna C. Bell]] |location= The Library of Congress}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2014}} |end_date={{End date|2015}} |event= [[Kathleen D. Roe]] |location= New York State Archives}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2015}} |end_date={{End date|2016}} |event= Dennis Meissner |location= Minnesota Historical Society}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2016}} |end_date={{End date|2017}} |event= [[Nancy McGovern]] |location= MIT}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2017}} |end_date={{End date|2018}} |event= [[Tanya Zanish-Belcher]] |location= Wake Forest University}}\n# {{Timeline-event|date={{Start date|2018}} |end_date={{End date|2019}} |event= [[Meredith Evans (archivist)|Meredith Evans]] |location= Jimmy Carter Presidential Library and Museum}}\n\n== Prior meetings<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www2.archivists.org/conference|title=SAA Annual Meeting|website=www2.archivists.org|accessdate=2018-07-23}}</ref> ==\n\nMeetings of the Society of American Archivists are often held jointly with other organizations such as the Council of State Archivists (CoSA), and the [[National Association of Government Archives and Records Administrators]] (NAGARA).\n\n{| class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible\"\n!Meeting\n!Date\n!Venue\n!Location\n!Theme\n!Joint meeting\n|-\n|83\n|2019 July 31-August 6\n|JW Marriott Austin\n|Austin, TX\n|ARCHIVES*RECORDS 2019\n|CoSA\n|-\n|82\n|2018 August 12-18\n|Marriott Wardman Park Hotel\n|Washington, DC\n|ARCHIVES*RECORDS 2018 \n|CoSA, NAGARA\n|-\n|81\n|2017 July 23-29 \n|Oregon Convention Center\n|Portland, OR\n|ARCHIVES 2017: alike/different\n|\n|-\n|80\n|2016 July 31-August 6\n|Hilton Atlanta\n|Atlanta, GA\n|ARCHIVES*RECORDS 2016\n|CoSA\n|-\n|79\n|2015 August 16-22\n|Cleveland Convention Center\n|Cleveland, OH\n|ARCHIVES 2015\n|\n|-\n|78\n|2014 August 10-16\n|Marriott Wardman Park Hotel\n|Washington, DC\n|ARCHIVES*RECORDS: Ensuring Access\n|CoSA, NAGARA\n|-\n|77\n|2013 August 11-17\n|Hilton New Orleans Riverside\n|New Orleans, LA\n|ARCHIVES New Orleans 2013\n|CoSA\n|-\n|76\n|2012 August 6-11\n|San Diego Hilton Bayfront\n|San Diego, CA\n|Beyond Borders: San Diego 2012\n|\n|-\n|75\n|2011 August 22-27\n|Hyatt Regency Chicago\n|Chicago, IL\n|ARCHIVES 360\u00b0\n|\n|-\n|74\n|2010 August 10-15\n|Marriott Wardman Park Hotel\n|Washington, DC\n|ARCHIVES*RECORDS / DC 2010\n|CoSA, NAGARA\n|-\n|73\n|2009 August 11-16\n|Hilton Austin\n|Austin, TX\n|Sustainable Archives: AUSTIN 2009\n|CoSA\n|-\n|72\n|2008 August 26-30\n|Hilton San Francisco\n|San Francisc